TY  - JOUR
T1  - Joint Pricing and Inventory Decisions for Constant Priced Items
AU  - Kunreuther, Howard
AU  - Schrage, Linus
Y1  - 1973/03/01
PY  - 1973
DA  - 1973/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.19.7.732
